Firstcorp Inc said its board hasincreased the maximum number of Class A shares in itsrepurchase program to 250,000 from 200,000 shares.    The program was first adopted in June 1986 and provided fora maximum of 100,000 shares to be repurchased through June1987.    In June 1986, the company increased the shares to 200,000and extended the period to end September 1987. Reuter&#3;